Injured by a police inspector during an interrogation, Abdel is at a hospital, almost dead. 
In the suburbs where he lives, some riots happened during the night, and one policeman lost his gun. One of Abdel's friends, Vinz, finds it. 
Vinz and his two pals, Said and Hubert, have nothing to do so they try to kill time. Vinz swears that if Abdel dies, he will shoot a policeman... 
-Written by Yepok-
